title: Acoustic Java
description: Serves meat, veg options available. Very veg-friendly coffeehouse featuring local artists. Offers meals such as veggie bacon cheeseburger, tempeh wrap, and tempeh reuben sandwich and can substitute with vegan cheese. Has soymilk and almond milk in coffee drinks, plus a modest selection of vegan baked goods like scones and chocolate chip banana bread. Hosts live music events.
